com.upsight.android.analytics.provider

Class UpsightDataProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.upsight.android.analytics.provider.UpsightDataProvider
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractUxmBlockProvider, AndroidIDBlockProvider, AppBlockProvider, DeviceBlockProvider, LocationBlockProvider, ScreenBlockProvider, SdkBlockProvider, SidProvider

    public abstract class UpsightDataProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that must be implemented by classes providing data to an Schema.

    All implementations should be thread safe because method will be called from different threads
